The Genting Snow Park in the Zhangjiakou competition zone will host para snowboard cross and para snowboard banked slalom with eight gold medals up for grabs. The conversion work at the venue been completed with training starting on Thursday.Eighty-one athletes will compete at the park and they have already begun adaptive training. After the conversion, the venue operation team tested the accessibility facilities with the newly added service center for wheelchairs and artificial limb repair also up and running. The Netherlands snowboarding coach Hansjoerg Berger is leading his team to get adjusted and says he is satisfied with the facilities.